high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the counter.
Grab the toilet paper from inside the cabinet under the counter.
Walk to the middle of the counter.
Place the toilet paper on the counter.
Turn around, then turn right and walk towards the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from next to the toilet.
Turn back around and walk back to the counter.
Place the toilet paper roll on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place two rolls of toilet paper, one full and one empty, on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the right most sink.
Open the cabinet on the right and grab the toilet paper.
Turn left and head to in-between both sinks.
Place the toilet paper in-between the two sinks.
Turn around then head right to the toilet.
Grab the empty toilet paper roll off of the floor.
Turn around and head back to in-between the sinks.
Place the empty roll behind the full toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Place the two rolls on the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the closest sink.
Take the toilet paper roll out of the right cabinet.
Take a step left.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter between the two sinks.
Turn around and veer right to the toilet.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the floor.
Turn around a veer left back to the sinks.
Put the empty toilet paper roll behind the full toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls on a desk.
